"\n"
"Try to distribute your products across your packages so that they weigh less "
"than %(max_weight)s %(unit)s or choose another carrier."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Trate de distribuir sus productos en varios paquetes para que pesen menos "
"de  %(max_weight)s %(unit)s o elija otro transportista."

